{
  "video_id": "cZe3zcNoIKk",
  "title": "How I'm using LEGO to teach Arabic | Ghada Wali",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12920.0,
      "end_time": 14320.0,
      "text": "I come from Egypt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15440.0,
      "end_time": 18880.0,
      "text": "which is also called Umm al-Dunya, the Mother of the World."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20840.0,
      "end_time": 23695.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a rich country filled with stories of rebellion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23720.0,
      "end_time": 27960.0,
      "text": "stories of civilizational triumph and downfall"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27120.0,
      "end_time": 28736.0,
      "text": "and the rich, religious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28760.0,
      "end_time": 32440.0,
      "text": "ethnic, cultural and linguistic diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33360.0,
      "end_time": 35536.0,
      "text": "Growing up in such an environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35560.0,
      "end_time": 38520.0,
      "text": "I became a strong believer in the power of storytelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39680.0,
      "end_time": 42696.0,
      "text": "As I searched for the medium with which to tell my story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42720.0,
      "end_time": 44560.0,
      "text": "I stumbled upon graphic design."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45640.0,
      "end_time": 47656.0,
      "text": "I would like to share with you a project"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47680.0,
      "end_time": 51336.0,
      "text": "of how graphic design can bring the Arabic language to life."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51360.0,
      "end_time": 53720.0,
      "text": "But first, let me tell you why I want to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54640.0,
      "end_time": 57480.0,
      "text": "I believe that graphic design can change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58120.0,
      "end_time": 60960.0,
      "text": "At least in my very own city of Cairo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60120.0,
      "end_time": 62919.0,
      "text": "it helped overthrow two separate dictators."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63840.0,
      "end_time": 65936.0,
      "text": "As you can see from those photos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65960.0,
      "end_time": 70336.0,
      "text": "the power and potential of graphic design as a tool for positive change"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70360.0,
      "end_time": 71800.0,
      "text": "is undeniably strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73440.0,
      "end_time": 77759.0,
      "text": "Egypt&#39;s 2011 revolution was also a grassroots design revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78600.0,
      "end_time": 80360.0,
      "text": "Everyone became a creator."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80920.0,
      "end_time": 83176.0,
      "text": "People were the real designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83200.0,
      "end_time": 84696.0,
      "text": "and, just overnight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84720.0,
      "end_time": 87295.0,
      "text": "Cairo was flooded with posters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87320.0,
      "end_time": 89399.0,
      "text": "signage, graffiti."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90800.0,
      "end_time": 91856.0,
      "text": "Visual communication"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91880.0,
      "end_time": 95560.0,
      "text": "was the medium that spoke far louder than words"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95800.0,
      "end_time": 99295.0,
      "text": "when the population of over 90 million voices were suppressed"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99320.0,
      "end_time": 100960.0,
      "text": "for almost 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 106496.0,
      "text": "It was precisely this political and social suppression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106520.0,
      "end_time": 109536.0,
      "text": "coupled with decades of colonialism"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109560.0,
      "end_time": 111336.0,
      "text": "and miseducation"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111360.0,
      "end_time": 115216.0,
      "text": "that slowly eroded the significance of the Arabic script in the region."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115240.0,
      "end_time": 117815.0,
      "text": "All of these countries once used Arabic."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117840.0,
      "end_time": 119602.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s just the green and the blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120960.0,
      "end_time": 122655.0,
      "text": "To put it simply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122680.0,
      "end_time": 124360.0,
      "text": "the Arabic script is dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125120.0,
      "end_time": 129735.0,
      "text": "In postcolonial Arab countries functioning in an increasingly globalized world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129758.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131296.0,
      "text": "it is a growing alarm"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131320.0,
      "end_time": 135200.0,
      "text": "that less and less people are using the Arabic script to communicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137720.0,
      "end_time": 142376.0,
      "text": "As I was studying my master&#39;s in Italy, I noticed myself missing Arabic."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142400.0,
      "end_time": 144336.0,
      "text": "I missed looking at the letters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144360.0,
      "end_time": 146176.0,
      "text": "digesting their meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146200.0,
      "end_time": 150536.0,
      "text": "So one day, I walked into one of the biggest libraries in Italy"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150560.0,
      "end_time": 152160.0,
      "text": "in search of an Arabic book."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152880.0,
      "end_time": 155536.0,
      "text": "I was surprised to find that this is what they had"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155560.0,
      "end_time": 158960.0,
      "text": "under the category of \"Arabic/Middle Eastern books.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161800.0,
      "end_time": 163496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163520.0,
      "end_time": 167360.0,
      "text": "Fear, terrorism and destruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168240.0,
      "end_time": 170000.0,
      "text": "One word: ISIS."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 171400.0,
      "end_time": 172656.0,
      "text": "My heart ached"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172680.0,
      "end_time": 174896.0,
      "text": "that this is how we are portrayed to the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174920.0,
      "end_time": 176959.0,
      "text": "even from a literary perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 177560.0,
      "end_time": 182160.0,
      "text": "I asked myself: Whatever happened to the world-renowned writers"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182400.0,
      "end_time": 185200.0,
      "text": "like Naguib Mahfouz, Khalil Gibran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186280.0,
      "end_time": 191200.0,
      "text": "iconic poets like Mutanabbi, Nizar Qabbani?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191880.0,
      "end_time": 193616.0,
      "text": "Think about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 193640.0,
      "end_time": 197655.0,
      "text": "The cultural products of an entire region of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 197680.0,
      "end_time": 199976.0,
      "text": "as rich, as diverse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200000.0,
      "end_time": 201560.0,
      "text": "have been deemed redundant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202560.0,
      "end_time": 204360.0,
      "text": "if not ignored altogether."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205880.0,
      "end_time": 209576.0,
      "text": "The cultural products of an entire region of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 209600.0,
      "end_time": 213376.0,
      "text": "have been barred from imparting any kind of real impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 213400.0,
      "end_time": 216640.0,
      "text": "on global media productions and contemporary social discourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 217440.0,
      "end_time": 219936.0,
      "text": "And then I reminded myself of my number one belief:"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 219960.0,
      "end_time": 222256.0,
      "text": "design can change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 222280.0,
      "end_time": 225136.0,
      "text": "All you need is for someone to catch a glimpse of your work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 225160.0,
      "end_time": 226720.0,
      "text": "feel, connect."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 227440.0,
      "end_time": 229000.0,
      "text": "And so I started."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 229600.0,
      "end_time": 233775.0,
      "text": "I thought about how can I stop the world from seeing us as evil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 233800.0,
      "end_time": 235936.0,
      "text": "as terrorists of this planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235960.0,
      "end_time": 239960.0,
      "text": "and start perceiving us as equals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 239120.0,
      "end_time": 240320.0,
      "text": "fellow humans?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241480.0,
      "end_time": 243816.0,
      "text": "How can I save and honor the Arabic script"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243840.0,
      "end_time": 246320.0,
      "text": "and share it with other people, other cultures?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247400.0,
      "end_time": 249136.0,
      "text": "And then it hit me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 249160.0,
      "end_time": 252976.0,
      "text": "What if I combined the two most significant symbols"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253000.0,
      "end_time": 256216.0,
      "text": "of innocence and Arab identity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 256240.0,
      "end_time": 258400.0,
      "text": "Maybe then people could resonate."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 259120.0,
      "end_time": 262656.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s more pure, innocent and fun as LEGO?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 262680.0,
      "end_time": 264256.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a universal child&#39;s toy."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 264280.0,
      "end_time": 267575.0,
      "text": "You play with them, you build with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 267600.0,
      "end_time": 270200.0,
      "text": "and with them, you imagine endless possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 271160.0,
      "end_time": 275616.0,
      "text": "My eureka moment was to find a bilingual solution for Arabic education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 275640.0,
      "end_time": 278296.0,
      "text": "because effective communication and education"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 278320.0,
      "end_time": 281960.0,
      "text": "is the road to more tolerant communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 281120.0,
      "end_time": 285416.0,
      "text": "However, the Arabic and Latin scripts do not only represent different worlds"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 285440.0,
      "end_time": 290160.0,
      "text": "but also create technical difficulties for both Eastern and Western communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 290400.0,
      "end_time": 291536.0,
      "text": "on a daily basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 291560.0,
      "end_time": 294456.0,
      "text": "There are so many reasons why Arabic and Latin are different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 294480.0,
      "end_time": 296176.0,
      "text": "but here are some of the main ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 296200.0,
      "end_time": 298896.0,
      "text": "Yes, both use upward and downward strokes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 298920.0,
      "end_time": 301200.0,
      "text": "but have completely different baselines."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302160.0,
      "end_time": 304416.0,
      "text": "Arabic tends to be more calligraphic"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 304440.0,
      "end_time": 307376.0,
      "text": "and connectivity is important to the Arabic language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 307400.0,
      "end_time": 311736.0,
      "text": "whose letters have to be mostly joined in order to articulate a given word."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 311760.0,
      "end_time": 316336.0,
      "text": "It also uses an entirely different system of punctuation and diacritics."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 316360.0,
      "end_time": 318416.0,
      "text": "But most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 318440.0,
      "end_time": 320576.0,
      "text": "Arabic has no capital letters."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 320600.0,
      "end_time": 323936.0,
      "text": "Instead it has four different letter forms:"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 323960.0,
      "end_time": 327200.0,
      "text": "initial, medial, isolated and final."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 328520.0,
      "end_time": 333376.0,
      "text": "I want to introduce the Arabic language to young learners, foreign speakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 333400.0,
      "end_time": 337440.0,
      "text": "but most importantly help refugees integrate to their host societies"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 339440.0,
      "end_time": 341896.0,
      "text": "through creating a bilingual learning system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 341920.0,
      "end_time": 344536.0,
      "text": "a two-way flow of communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 344560.0,
      "end_time": 346160.0,
      "text": "And I called it \"Let&#39;s Play.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 348160.0,
      "end_time": 352816.0,
      "text": "The idea is to simply create a fun and engaging way of learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 352840.0,
      "end_time": 355000.0,
      "text": "Modern Standard Arabic through LEGO."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 355840.0,
      "end_time": 358496.0,
      "text": "These are the two words. \"Let&#39;s Play.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358520.0,
      "end_time": 361200.0,
      "text": "Every colored bar marks an Arabic letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 362800.0,
      "end_time": 366376.0,
      "text": "As you can see, the letter is explained in form, sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 366400.0,
      "end_time": 368816.0,
      "text": "and examples of words in function,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 368840.0,
      "end_time": 371455.0,
      "text": "in addition to the equivalent in Latin."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371480.0,
      "end_time": 373736.0,
      "text": "Together, they form a fun pocket book"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 373760.0,
      "end_time": 377216.0,
      "text": "with the 29 Arabic letters and the four different forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 377240.0,
      "end_time": 379160.0,
      "text": "plus a 400-word dictionary."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 380160.0,
      "end_time": 381936.0,
      "text": "So this is how the page looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 381960.0,
      "end_time": 384416.0,
      "text": "You have the letter, the transliteration in Latin"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 384440.0,
      "end_time": 386120.0,
      "text": "and the description underneath."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 387200.0,
      "end_time": 388820.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll take you through the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 389520.0,
      "end_time": 391656.0,
      "text": "So first in my tiny studio in Florence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 391680.0,
      "end_time": 393136.0,
      "text": "I built the letters."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 393160.0,
      "end_time": 395976.0,
      "text": "I photographed each letter separately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 396000.0,
      "end_time": 399976.0,
      "text": "and then I retouched every letter and chose the correct color background"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 400000.0,
      "end_time": 401440.0,
      "text": "and typefaces to use."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 402320.0,
      "end_time": 405135.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, I created the full letter set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 405160.0,
      "end_time": 408656.0,
      "text": "which is 29 letters times four different forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 408680.0,
      "end_time": 411760.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s 116 letters build just in one week."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 413000.0,
      "end_time": 417320.0,
      "text": "I believe that information should and can be fun, portable."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 418400.0,
      "end_time": 420616.0,
      "text": "This book is the final product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 420640.0,
      "end_time": 422976.0,
      "text": "which I would eventually like to publish"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 423000.0,
      "end_time": 426416.0,
      "text": "and translate into as many languages in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 426440.0,
      "end_time": 432520.0,
      "text": "so that Arabic teaching and learning becomes fun, easy and accessible globally."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 433520.0,
      "end_time": 437719.0,
      "text": "With this book, I hope to save my nation&#39;s beautiful script."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 438480.0,
      "end_time": 442936.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 442960.0,
      "end_time": 444159.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 447120.0,
      "end_time": 452160.0,
      "text": "Working on this project was a form of visual meditation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 452400.0,
      "end_time": 453296.0,
      "text": "like a Sufi dance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 453320.0,
      "end_time": 455159.0,
      "text": "a prayer to a better planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 455920.0,
      "end_time": 459536.0,
      "text": "One set of building blocks made two languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 459560.0,
      "end_time": 461160.0,
      "text": "LEGO is just a metaphor."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 461960.0,
      "end_time": 465215.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because we are all made of the same building unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 465240.0,
      "end_time": 467136.0,
      "text": "is that I can see a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 467160.0,
      "end_time": 468960.0,
      "text": "where the barriers between people"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 469960.0,
      "end_time": 471400.0,
      "text": "all come tumbling down."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 472160.0,
      "end_time": 475456.0,
      "text": "So no matter how ugly the world around us gets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 475480.0,
      "end_time": 479960.0,
      "text": "or how many discouraging books on ISIS, the terrorist group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 479120.0,
      "end_time": 482296.0,
      "text": "and not Isis, the ancient Egyptian goddess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 482320.0,
      "end_time": 484296.0,
      "text": "continue to be published,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 484320.0,
      "end_time": 486960.0,
      "text": "I will keep building one colorful world."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 488120.0,
      "end_time": 490136.0,
      "text": "Shukran, which means \"thank you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 490160.0,
      "end_time": 492776.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 492800.0,
      "end_time": 495416.0,
      "text": "Thank you. Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 495440.0,
      "end_time": 496640.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}